

=Description=

"Impact licensing is a strategic instrument to optimise the valorisation potential of technologies and data without
losing sight of the economic dimension. ILI’s main goal is to take up the gap in today’s licensing practices that
either consist of purely for-profit oriented licences, or licences that are solely societal value oriented via free
licences or licensing waivers."

(https://impactlicensing.eu)


